            <title>[HBASE-10776] Separate HConnectionManager into several parts</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-10776</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;HConnectionManager is too large to effectively maintain. This Jira records some refactoring jobs:&lt;/p&gt;

